Visualisation application for BLUE CPU emulator

	Shows you the current state of the CPUs registers and RAM in the fancy way.
Allows to control CPU directly.

Uses:
- Blue CPU emulator: https://github.com/msun-dev/cpu-blue
- Raylib (GUI): https://github.com/raysan5/raylib

To build:
- Linux: Be sure that you have raylib library installed (static).
		Then do `./scripts/build.sh`
- Windows: Not possible yet
- WASM: Not possible yet
